{
  "stem": "15115.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, don't worry about it [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We'll go to the baustelle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As soon as we were going to the baustelle, he says, here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll give you a stick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Go to the bathroom where the people go to the washroom to, you know-- there's no washroom, just an open pit, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You [INAUDIBLE] and then I'll come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But an hour later, I'll come and take you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'll pick you up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the baustelle was a barrack called Red Cross barrack in case of-- so he comes-- he comes in with two guys.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he brings me out a white towel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wraps it all over my face.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two guys are carrying me, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he takes me to the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, sleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'll wake you up tomorrow morning and take you back to camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then that's where the hard work that I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I used to help everybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all the Greeks in Israel and in Greece, wherever they are, they all know me because what I did for them when I had the position, you see?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And like this, this Greek boy survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Took us quite a while, and all of a sudden, we hear that the-- what do you call?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were in Waldlager, which is already in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Russians coming in and bombing the whole place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, we could see at night, they put what do you call, those lights, to make it-- Floodlights.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Floodlights to throw the bombs out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could see it was coming to the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But still, we have no news.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have no news, but we can see already there is no Auschwitz and there's no Birkenau, because there's on crematoriums where we are.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
